					<div>    3 (0x3)	Running or Full Power</div>
					<div>    4 (0x4)	Warning</div>
					<div>    5 (0x5)	In Test</div>
					<div>    6 (0x6)	Not Applicable</div>
					<div>    7 (0x7)	Power Off</div>
					<div>    8 (0x8)	Off Line</div>
					<div>    9 (0x9)	Off Duty</div>
					<div>    10 (0xA)	Degraded</div>
