					<div>    The device is not functioning, but could be brought to full p=
ower quickly.</div>
					<div>    16 (0x10)	Power Cycle</div>
					<div>    17 (0x11)	Power Save - Warning</div>
					<div>    The device is in a warning state, though also in a power save=
