	<p>This table contains information about the attributes and behaviors of a=
 network adapter. It only stores Windows computer data pulled from the Win3=
2_NetworkAdapterConfiguration WMI class. More info on this class can be fou=
nd here: <a href=3D"http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/aa394217%28v=3D=
