o indicate that the object is installed.</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<th>LargeSystemCache</th>
				<td class=3D"type">bit</td>
				<td class=3D"null">=E2=98=92</td>
				<td><div>Beginning with Windows Vista, this property is obsolete and no=
t supported.</div>
					<div>    Value	Meaning</div>
					<div>    0                Optimize memory for applications.</div>
					<div>    1                Optimize memory for system performance.</div=
>
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<th>MaxProcessMemorySize</th>
