	<h2 id=3D"tblOSRecoveryConfiguration" data-cy=3D"tblOSRecoveryConfiguratio=
n"><a href=3D"http://10.10.201.22:81/Report/DatabaseDocumentation.aspx#toc"=
 class=3D"tocref">=E2=87=A7</a>tblOSRecoveryConfiguration</h2>
	<p>This table contains the types of information that will be gathered from=
