 SNMP matches the MAC address of a scanned asset, the Network Interfaces se=
ction of the switch page will link to the Lansweeper webpage of the connect=
ed asset. If the connected asset has not been scanned by Lansweeper, only t=
he MAC address pulled from SNMP will be displayed on the switch page.</p>
