=A8 <a href=3D"http://10.10.201.22:81/Report/DatabaseDocumentation.aspx#tbl=
Assets">tblAssets</a>.AssetID</span>FK</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<th>IfIndex</th>
				<td class=3D"type">int</td>
				<td class=3D"null">=E2=98=90</td>
				<td>Interface/port number.</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<th>AssetMacAddress</th>
				<td class=3D"type">varchar</td>
				<td class=3D"null">=E2=98=90</td>
				<td>MAC address of the last asset to be detected on (connected to) the =
interface/port. If the connected asset has been scanned by Lansweeper as we=
ll, this field can be linked to the Mac field of tblAssetMacAddress, which =
